General.Name: Northgold AB
General.Description: Northgold AB (publ) operates as a gold exploration and development company in Sweden. Its flagship project is the Kopsa gold and copper project located in the Middle Ostrobothnia Gold Belt of Central Finland. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
